title: Aleister Crowley - Gems from the Equinox (fixed)
description: This is a cleaned up version of Aleister Crowley: Gems from the Equinox. The original version I downloaded a while back had extremely messy and incomplete metadata, with incorrect author tagging and mostly random filenames. I spent a few hours correcting this, so enjoy a cleaned up, eBook reader-ready collection of Aleister Crowley's semi-complete works!
